org.forgerock.opendj.server.config.server

Interface ChangeNumberControlPluginCfg

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Configuration, PluginCfg

    public interface ChangeNumberControlPluginCfg
extends PluginCfg
    A server-side interface for querying Change Number Control Plugin settings.

    The Change Number Control Plugin returns the change number generated by the replication subsystem.
